{
  "stem": "19231.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 422.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the way-- can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the way, when we stopped-- I don't know where it was-- but it was on the way going to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was another [NON-ENGLISH]-- another-- they called them [NON-ENGLISH], a [NON-ENGLISH], like another train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I saw my sister and her family on the opposite side from us, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to get together so much with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they wouldn't let us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they said, you all go be in one place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I never saw her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did your--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was coincidence that I saw her, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was with my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we wanted so much to get together, but was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- I didn't feel any cruelty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Siberia, we had-- like, there were-- there was like a little village, must be like an army barracks or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every-- two families got one little room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was nothing in the room, except two, like, from wooden made beds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I slept with my both parents in one bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there is-- they put another family, a man with two sons, in the same room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no kitchen, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to go and get-- there-- they had a big kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they gave us a card.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we used to get once a day soup and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't remember quarter of a pound, you know, of bread a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's how it was, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And sometimes, we-- my mother and I, we used to go in the little villages in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The snow was so high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We used to just go in with one leg and out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we used to dig and go for a potato or for a cabbage.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
